    "name": "Majjiga Pulusu",
    "description": "A soothing Andhra-style Majjiga Charu made with freshly whisked buttermilk, crushed ginger, green chilli, and aromatic tempering for a light yet deeply comforting flavor. Gently heated with onions, garlic, curry leaves, and spices, this warm homestyle classic pairs beautifully with hot rice for a simple soulful meal.\n",
